<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.5">
<l>accuta ṉamala ṉeṉkō vaṭiyavar viṉaike ṭukku</l>
<l>naccumā marunta meṉkō nalaṅkaṭa lamuta meṉkō</l>
<l>vaccuvaik kaṭṭi yeṉkō vaṟucuvai yaṭici leṉkō</l>
<l>neyccuvait tēṟa leṉkō kaṉiyeṉkō pāleṉ kēṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “unshakable on, spotless one”? Will I say “desired great remedy</l>
<l>that destroys the devotees’ karma”? Will I say “ocean of goodness, ambrosia”?</l>
<l>Will I say “well-tasting sweets”? Will I say “rice with six tastes”?</l>
<l>Will I say “clarified sap with butter taste”? Will I say “ripe fruit”? do I say “milk”?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
